\/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Discover how clear career paths eliminate uncertainty and show employees exactly where their hard work can lead, boosting morale and productivity.<\/span><p>\u00a0<\/p><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Showcase Options<\/b><b><br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Explore how offering multiple career pathways\u2014technical, leadership, project management, and more\u2014empowers your employees with flexibility and choice, building loyalty and long-term commitment.<\/span><p>\u00a0<\/p><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Demonstrate Support<\/b><b><br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Learn how to align learning and development initiatives with career paths to show employees you\u2019re invested in their growth and success.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/><\/span><\/li><\/ol><h3><b>Who Should Attend?<\/b><\/h3><p><b><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This webinar is perfect for leaders in AEC firms who want to create a roadmap for organizational and employee success. Gain actionable insights to position your firm as a top employer, attract high-caliber talent, and retain your existing team by fostering a culture of clarity, options, and support.<\/span><\/p><h3><b>Seats are limited!<\/b><\/h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Take the first step in guiding your team out of the fog. Sign up for this free webinar today and start building the career pathways that will drive your firm forward.<\/span><\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"section"},{"id":"5ecb3efd","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Your Presenter<\/b><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"182c4be5","settings":{"editor":"<h2 class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM | Engineering Management Institute<\/b><\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"ee11555","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-55130 size-medium\" title=\"Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"EMI- Your Engineering Career\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most AEC organizations are too busy to focus on attracting, developing, and retaining talented professionals, making it hard to grow. Through his work a tEMI, Fasano utilizes a proven framework to help organizations, both public and private, build professional development plans, programs, and tools that help them attract, build, AND maintain strong teams and grow sustainably.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fasano has written a bestselling book entitled <\/span><b><i>Engineer Your Own Success <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(by IEEE-Wiley Press)<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and under his stewardship, EMI has built a massive content platform including 10 active podcasts, 3 YouTube channels, and a popular blog dedicated to helping AEC professionals become better managers and leaders.<\/span><\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"50","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"}],"settings":{"template":"elementor_canvas"},"metadata":{"_yoast_wpseo_content_score":"60","be_title_toggle_hide":"1","_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes":"3","disable_sitewide_popup":"a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"true\";}","_yoast_wpseo_wordproof_timestamp":"","_yoast_wpseo_meta-robots-noindex":"1","_yoast_wpseo_meta-robots-nofollow":"1"}}